text: Liubym Kohan (born 2 July 1975) is a Ukrainian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Ukraine Category:Ski jumpers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Chernivtsi
